Package Management:
  Install/update packages: apt/yum/dnf install <package>
File and Directory Management:
  List files: ls
  Move/copy/remove files: mv/cp/rm
  Text Manipulation:
  Search text: grep <pattern> <file>
  Filter/transform text: awk/sed
Process Management:
  View processes: ps
  Top processes: top
  Kill a process: kill <PID>
Networking:
  Display network interfaces: ifconfig/ip
  Network statistics: netstat -a
  Trace route: traceroute <hostname or IP>
  Network discovery: nmap <hostname or IP>
  Packet analyzer: tcpdump -i <interface>
  Bandwidth monitoring: iftop
  DNS query: dig/nslookup
  Connection information: ss -tulwn
  IP routing table: ip route show
  Firewall configuration: iptables -L
Performance Monitoring Tools:
  Resource usage statistics: vmstat
  Disk I/O statistics: iostat
  Memory usage: free -m
  Disk space usage: df -h
  Network interface statistics: sar -n DEV 1 5
  Monitoring and Visualization:
Monitoring and Logging:
  Tail logs: tail -f <file>
  Grep in logs: grep <pattern> <file>
  System journal: journalctl -u <unit>
  Monitor system metrics: htop
SSH:
  Secure remote connection: ssh <user>@<hostname>
  Copy files securely: scp <file> <user>@<hostname>:<destination>
Version Control:
  Git commands: git clone/pull/commit
Containerization:
  Docker commands: docker run/ps
Orchestration:
  Kubernetes commands: kubectl get/apply
Automation:
  Ansible playbook: ansible-playbook <playbook.yml>
  Infrastructure as Code (IaC):
  Terraform commands: terraform init/apply
  Prometheus/Grafana: systemctl start prometheus
